/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}, {\"begin\": 7807, \"end\": 7812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vaast\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\"}, {\"begin\": 7888, \"end\": 7895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huahine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Huahine\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huahine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huahine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a population\", \"from\": 7752, \"to\": 7764}, {\"ngram\": \"one female\", \"from\": 7818, \"to\": 7828}, {\"ngram\": \"Vahine Fierro\", \"from\": 7830, \"to\": 7843}, {\"ngram\": \"the nearby island\", \"from\": 7867, \"to\": 7884}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 7911, \"to\": 7923}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What made their achievement even more remarkable was that they did so not through WSL rankings but via the2024 International Surfing Association (ISA) World Surfing Gamesin El Salvador.\", \"from\": 7925, \"to\": 8110, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8007, \"end\": 8010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.376168776980133e-62, \"text\": \"WSL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\"}, {\"begin\": 8036, \"end\": 8069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Surfing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Surfing Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Surfing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Surfing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 8098, \"end\": 8109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/El_Salvador\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.595858357996652e-16, \"text\": \"El Salvador\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/El_Salvador\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/El_Salvador\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their achievement\", \"from\": 7935, \"to\": 7952}, {\"ngram\": \"the2024\", \"from\": 8028, \"to\": 8035}, {\"ngram\": \"ISA\", \"from\": 8071, \"to\": 8074}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The World Surfing Gamesare a bit of a lotterywith many of the world's best surfers being knocked out by lesser names.\", \"from\": 8111, \"to\": 8228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8121, \"end\": 8128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surfing\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0802711138955723e-62, \"text\": \"Surfing\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surfing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surfing\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 8138, \"to\": 8143}, {\"ngram\": \"a lotterywith\", \"from\": 8147, \"to\": 8160}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's best surfers\", \"from\": 8169, \"to\": 8193}, {\"ngram\": \"lesser names\", \"from\": 8215, \"to\": 8227}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What's more, \\\"the conditions were completely different to what they are used to,\\\" says McKenna, who was in El Salvador for the competition.\", \"from\": 8229, \"to\": 8368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8336, \"end\": 8347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/El_Salvador\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.595858357996652e-16, \"text\": \"El Salvador\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/El_Salvador\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/El_Salvador\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the conditions\", \"from\": 8243, \"to\": 8257}, {\"ngram\": \"McKenna\", \"from\": 8316, \"to\": 8323}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 8352, \"to\": 8367}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was incredible how it happened, that both Kauli and Vahine qualified.\\\"\", \"from\": 8369, \"to\": 8443, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both Kauli\", \"from\": 8410, \"to\": 8420}, {\"ngram\": \"Vahine\", \"from\": 8425, \"to\": 8431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now that they have qualified, home ground advantage makes both Vaast and Fierro serious gold medal contenders, especially if the waves are big and hollow.\", \"from\": 8445, \"to\": 8599, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8508, \"end\": 8513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vaast\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"home ground advantage\", \"from\": 8475, \"to\": 8496}, {\"ngram\": \"Fierro serious gold medal contenders\", \"from\": 8518, \"to\": 8554}, {\"ngram\": \"the waves\", \"from\": 8570, \"to\": 8579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To underline this point, Fierro won the Teahupo'o leg of the 2024 WSL Championship Tour as a wildcard, beating the world's best surfers in massive waves on a day that's been widely acknowledged as \\\"one of the best days yet of women's contest surfing\\\".\", \"from\": 8600, \"to\": 8851, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 8613, \"to\": 8623}, {\"ngram\": \"Fierro\", \"from\": 8625, \"to\": 8631}, {\"ngram\": \"the Teahupo'o leg\", \"from\": 8636, \"to\": 8653}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 WSL Championship Tour\", \"from\": 8657, \"to\": 8687}, {\"ngram\": \"a wildcard\", \"from\": 8691, \"to\": 8701}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's best surfers\", \"from\": 8711, \"to\": 8735}, {\"ngram\": \"massive waves\", \"from\": 8739, \"to\": 8752}, {\"ngram\": \"a day\", \"from\": 8756, \"to\": 8761}, {\"ngram\": \"the best days\", \"from\": 8805, \"to\": 8818}, {\"ngram\": \"women's contest surfing\", \"from\": 8826, \"to\": 8849}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For a while it seemed like the Tahitian government's plans to build an aluminium judging tower that complied with the International Olympic Committee's health and safety regulations might be more of a threat to holding the contest at Teahupo'o than any anti-France sentiments.\", \"from\": 8853, \"to\": 9129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8884, \"end\": 8892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5833238882258081e-38, \"text\": \"Tahitian\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}, {\"begin\": 8971, \"end\": 9002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an aluminium judging tower\", \"from\": 8921, \"to\": 8947}, {\"ngram\": \"a threat\", \"from\": 9052, \"to\": 9060}, {\"ngram\": \"the contest\", \"from\": 9072, \"to\": 9083}, {\"ngram\": \"any anti-France sentiments\", \"from\": 9102, \"to\": 9128}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Apetition,championed by some big names in international surfing, argued that the tower would cause untold damage to the reef and called for the old, wooden tower to be used instead.\", \"from\": 9130, \"to\": 9311, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some big names\", \"from\": 9154, \"to\": 9168}, {\"ngram\": \"international surfing\", \"from\": 9172, \"to\": 9193}, {\"ngram\": \"the tower\", \"from\": 9207, \"to\": 9216}, {\"ngram\": \"untold damage\", \"from\": 9229, \"to\": 9242}, {\"ngram\": \"the reef\", \"from\": 9246, \"to\": 9254}, {\"ngram\": \"the old, wooden tower\", \"from\": 9270, \"to\": 9291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The waves are a 15-minute paddle from land, so judges do need a base nearby: Both the old and new towers are temporary structures that are assembled before a contest begins and removed when it finishes.\", \"from\": 9313, \"to\": 9515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The waves\", \"from\": 9313, \"to\": 9322}, {\"ngram\": \"a 15-minute paddle\", \"from\": 9327, \"to\": 9345}, {\"ngram\": \"land\", \"from\": 9351, \"to\": 9355}, {\"ngram\": \"judges\", \"from\": 9360, \"to\": 9366}, {\"ngram\": \"a base\", \"from\": 9375, \"to\": 9381}, {\"ngram\": \"Both the old and new towers\", \"from\": 9390, \"to\": 9417}, {\"ngram\": \"temporary structures\", \"from\": 9422, \"to\": 9442}, {\"ngram\": \"a contest\", \"from\": 9469, \"to\": 9478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After a barge involved in the new tower's construction struck the reef in December, the brouhaha ramped up several notches.\", \"from\": 9517, \"to\": 9640, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a barge\", \"from\": 9523, \"to\": 9530}, {\"ngram\": \"the new tower's construction\", \"from\": 9543, \"to\": 9571}, {\"ngram\": \"the reef\", \"from\": 9579, \"to\": 9587}, {\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 9591, \"to\": 9599}, {\"ngram\": \"the brouhaha\", \"from\": 9601, \"to\": 9613}, {\"ngram\": \"several notches\", \"from\": 9624, \"to\": 9639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When the ISA publicly opposed the tower's construction, the event seemed in serious jeopardy.\", \"from\": 9641, \"to\": 9734, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ISA\", \"from\": 9646, \"to\": 9653}, {\"ngram\": \"the tower's construction\", \"from\": 9671, \"to\": 9695}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 9697, \"to\": 9706}, {\"ngram\": \"serious jeopardy\", \"from\": 9717, \"to\": 9733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But thanks in part to the French Polynesian president, Moetai Brotherson - whoexpressed solidarity with the protestersand a willingness to move the contest to a nearby beach break - a compromise was reached.\", \"from\": 9735, \"to\": 9942, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9761, \"end\": 9788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_French_Polynesia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French Polynesian president\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_French_Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_French_Polynesia\"}, {\"begin\": 9761, \"end\": 9788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_French_Polynesia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French Polynesian president\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_French_Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_French_Polynesia\"}, {\"begin\": 9790, \"end\": 9807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moetai_Brotherson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Moetai Brotherson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moetai_Brotherson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moetai_Brotherson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thanks\", \"from\": 9739, \"to\": 9745}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 9749, \"to\": 9753}, {\"ngram\": \"the protestersand\", \"from\": 9839, \"to\": 9856}, {\"ngram\": \"the contest\", \"from\": 9879, \"to\": 9890}, {\"ngram\": \"a nearby beach break - a compromise\", \"from\": 9894, \"to\": 9929}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asmaller tower with far less environmental impacthas now been completed and was used in the WSL event in May.\", \"from\": 9944, \"to\": 10053, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10036, \"end\": 10039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.376168776980133e-62, \"text\": \"WSL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Asmaller tower\", \"from\": 9944, \"to\": 9958}, {\"ngram\": \"far less environmental impacthas\", \"from\": 9964, \"to\": 9996}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 10049, \"to\": 10052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The foundations are half the size they would have been,\\\" McKenna says.\", \"from\": 10054, \"to\": 10125, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The foundations\", \"from\": 10055, \"to\": 10070}, {\"ngram\": \"half the size\", \"from\": 10075, \"to\": 10088}, {\"ngram\": \"McKenna\", \"from\": 10112, \"to\": 10119}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And they are located in an area where there is very little coral.\\\"\", \"from\": 10126, \"to\": 10193, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an area\", \"from\": 10151, \"to\": 10158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the original plans involved digging an undersea trench to house water pipes and electricity and internet cables, now the pipes and cables are simply laid on the seabed during each contest and removed when it finishes.\", \"from\": 10194, \"to\": 10417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the original plans\", \"from\": 10200, \"to\": 10218}, {\"ngram\": \"an undersea trench\", \"from\": 10236, \"to\": 10254}, {\"ngram\": \"house water pipes\", \"from\": 10258, \"to\": 10275}, {\"ngram\": \"electricity and internet cables\", \"from\": 10280, \"to\": 10311}, {\"ngram\": \"the pipes\", \"from\": 10317, \"to\": 10326}, {\"ngram\": \"cables\", \"from\": 10331, \"to\": 10337}, {\"ngram\": \"the seabed\", \"from\": 10357, \"to\": 10367}, {\"ngram\": \"each contest\", \"from\": 10375, \"to\": 10387}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both McKenna and Brotherson agree that the protesters' concerns were justified but they are equally convinced that the new tower will be good for the island.\", \"from\": 10419, \"to\": 10576, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Both McKenna\", \"from\": 10419, \"to\": 10431}, {\"ngram\": \"Brotherson\", \"from\": 10436, \"to\": 10446}, {\"ngram\": \"the protesters' concerns\", \"from\": 10458, \"to\": 10482}, {\"ngram\": \"the new tower\", \"from\": 10534, \"to\": 10547}, {\"ngram\": \"the island\", \"from\": 10565, \"to\": 10575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The tower is not just for the Olympics,\\\" McKenna says.\", \"from\": 10577, \"to\": 10632, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The tower\", \"from\": 10578, \"to\": 10587}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 10604, \"to\": 10616}, {\"ngram\": \"McKenna\", \"from\": 10619, \"to\": 10626}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It can be used at contests for the next 20 years.\\\"\", \"from\": 10633, \"to\": 10684, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"contests\", \"from\": 10652, \"to\": 10660}, {\"ngram\": \"the next 20 years\", \"from\": 10665, \"to\": 10682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's hoped that the state-of-the-art tower - which, importantly, can now be insured for workplace safety - will persuade the WSL to keep coming back to Teahupo'o.\", \"from\": 10685, \"to\": 10847, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10810, \"end\": 10813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.376168776980133e-62, \"text\": \"WSL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the-art\", \"from\": 10714, \"to\": 10721}, {\"ngram\": \"workplace safety\", \"from\": 10773, \"to\": 10789}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(These concerns are justified: This year, South Africa's Jeffrey's Bay, another of the world's best waves and a Championship Tour stalwart for decades, was dropped from the WSL's flagship tour, seemingly due to the regional tourism board'sreluctance to bankroll the event.)\", \"from\": 10848, \"to\": 11121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10890, \"end\": 10902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7072059014189976e-15, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.or